## How to Test:

1. Enter amount in TRY in the wallet deposit modal
2. Use MasterCard: 5528790000000008
3. Enter CVV: 123, Expiry: 12/30
4. When 3D Secure prompt appears, enter: 123456
5. Payment should succeed!

## Notes:
- Iyzico sandbox requires EXACT test card numbers
- Any other card will result in FAILURE status
- 3D Secure password is always: 123456
- Test transactions won't charge real money
